The paper discusses the challenges of reproducing scientific discoveries in the research community, which is a common issue in software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed infrastructure involves automating the build, unit testing, and benchmarking of research software, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL), cybernetics (cs.CY), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and digital libraries (cs.DL).
